INSERT INTO auth_refresh_tokens (
                user_id,
                device_session_id,
                session_id,
                token_hash,
                issued_at,
                expires_at,
                metadata,
                device_name,
                family_id,
                generation
            )
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, '{}'::jsonb, NULL, $7, $8)
            RETURNING id
